@Yaqiongchai 
It's best to use the Mask Dataset provided by Liu et al. and make sure to download their [Testing Irregular Mask Dataset](http://masc.cs.gmu.edu/wiki/uploads/partialconv/mask.zip). The dataset contains 12,000 masks and you can easily augment it to 98,000 by rotation and reflection.

Still don't know why it stops after 1,000th epoch! Is it halting or ends with the message "_End training...._" ?
